{"tid":306913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7.1籌得50.8萬　社民連成政黨吸金王","createTime":"2017-07-03T02:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T02:59:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"07cf2b9634690df0a2f1be26bf92cc7f2480ce92","tid":306913,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:17:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20077182&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170703\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20077182%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170703&d=eqWqtdaGThpQqt3I9YvX9Z4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=6939cd59\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20077182%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170703&h=4557b239\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20077182&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170703</a><br />\n<br />\n7.1籌得50.8萬　社民連成政黨吸金王<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n社民連籌款數目逆市上升，成為7.1最吸金政黨。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今年民陣主辦的7.1遊行，人數比起去年減少近一半，泛民政黨籌款數字普遍較去年遜色，但部份有官司在身的政黨，籌款數字逆市上升，其中於7.1升旗禮請願時，被拉上警車踢下體的吳文遠，其任主席的社民連籌得50.8萬元，比去年增加8.8萬元，取代香港眾志成為今年7.1政黨吸金王；而為傘運被檢控人士籌款的守護公義基金則籌得54萬元，可見政府針對傘運組織者提出檢控等，引起市民關注及支援。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨籌款暴跌<br />\n<br />\n幾個泛民政黨的籌款數字均較去年下跌。公民黨去年籌得44.1萬元，今年籌款暴跌至只有約26萬元；民主黨籌款數字則與去年相若，有17.3萬元，只較去年7.1少了2,000元；人民力量及工黨今年分別籌到約16萬元及12.8萬元，分別較去年少了4萬元及1.6萬元。<br />\n當中民主黨、工黨已經表明，於扣除成本以及將十分一籌得款項上繳給民陣之後，餘下的款項將會全數撥予守護公義基金；公民黨執委會亦會討論籌得款項是否捐予該基金。而香港眾志立法會議員羅冠聰被政府司法覆核議席，該組織多名成員亦因為參與社運而有官司在身，籌款數字雖然不及去年的50萬元，但仍有43.2萬元。<br />\n專業議政姚松炎及邵家臻同樣面臨DQ官司，同屬該組織的議員梁繼昌亦因對UGL案窮追不捨而被前特首梁振英控告誹謗，結果專業議政初次籌款亦有19.2萬元。專業議政會向民陣捐出10%籌得款項，並在扣除街站運作成本後，全數存入核心價值基金，支援梁繼昌、邵家臻及姚松炎面對法律訴訟的費用。同樣面臨DQ官司的劉小麗則以小麗民主教室名義籌到19萬元。民陣則尚未完成點算捐款數字。<br />\n■記者陳雪玲<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n97年主權移交至今，香港前進還是倒退？「蘋果」與你細數廿載風雨。<br />\n【回歸二十年】專頁：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhksar20.appledaily.com.hk&d=eqWqtdaGThpQqt3I9YvX9Z4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=593a58dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk</a>￼"},{"pid":"71c07c688771b995d13f26d17d4c471bda150236","tid":306913,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170703/large/a0305a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170703%2Flarge%2Fa0305a.gif&h=483aff88&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86c8b3fa06f0bce18309033e42a6458dd2639fd1","tid":306913,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:20:50.000Z","msg":"白鴿黨冇左2千萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a1c01dc902988f34239184626f7abcd0b8bd1e","tid":306913,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:37:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>白鴿黨冇左2千萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278add261c6f41943827890c657d67bbbe1188ad","tid":306913,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:38:34.000Z","msg":"大將軍好波"},{"pid":"5c6858450ddee5d386af8fb326a71e303788e092","tid":306913,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:52:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8a9958ffff70ae2157c685cf82f291f8b1cddcc","tid":306913,"uid":42967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:55:12.000Z","msg":"熱血公民無報數?"},{"pid":"c5fa8012a491709624be7eb3b3